  "properties": {
    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "##  🔍Teacher Tip\r\nThis prompt allows students to begin to explore AI's assumptions. You will analyze AI's initial responses, identify potential **biases**, and refine your prompts to create more neutral and inclusive descriptions.\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background-color: #B7E0E5; border-radius: 10px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px auto; max-width: 85%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 14pt; margin-top: 12px; line-height: 120%;\">📖 <strong>AI Bias</strong> occurs when a model favors certain information over others..</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; background-color: #F5F7F8; padding: 10px; border-left: 5px solid #8148B2; display: inline-block;\">➡️ This activity is from Lesson 6. You can find more details in the full <a href='https://studio.code.org/s/aif1-2025/lessons/6' target='_blank' rel='noopener noreferrer' style='text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;'>Lesson Plan</a>.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n\r\n## Career Clothing\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to provide a description of an appropriate outfit for each career.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n1. **Copy and paste** the prompt below into AI Chat and press **Send**: \r\n\r\n>What should a secretary wear?\r\n2. Then **copy and paste** the prompt below into AI Chat and press **Send**: \r\n\r\n>What should a CEO wear?\r\n3. Compare **AI Chat's responses**. Discuss:\r\n    - Did AI Chat assume a default identity in either of the prompts?\r\n    - Did AI Chat's responses differ in the tone, assumptions, or characteristics it included?\r\n4. Refine one of the prompts above to reduce bias in the AI-generated response.\r\n\r\n::: details [Not sure how to refine your prompt?]\r\n- Try instructing AI to consider a diverse set of people in its description.\r\n- Give AI an example of how you would describe someone in this profession.\r\n:::",
